school or work, think about your claim or position, the reasons for the claim, and the evidence to support the claim.&nbsp;<br /><br />To make your argument even stronger, think about some of the ways someone could challenge you (rebut your argument), and then try to answer or counter that rebuttal.&nbsp;<br /><br />You may find that you need to go back and revise your original claim, because you&#39;ve found a weakness in it.&nbsp; That&#39;s great!
